{"tid":1598320,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"去對話OK 但唔該一定要講五大訴求同強調真普選","createTime":"2019-09-27T11:25:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T13:00:07.000Z","uid":104425,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"5bbb179ed6411b1be2e2f4c1fff7a7543af0fbc2","tid":1598320,"uid":104425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:25:31.000Z","msg":"「社區對話」劇本，愈來愈少黃發言，成功透過對言解決分歧，成立獨立調查員會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1598173\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1598173</a><br />\n<br />\n講真<br />\n完全杯葛佢係理想化做法<br />\n但隔離post巴打講咗<br />\n呢d show係做俾淺黃中立撚睇<br />\n既然有個咁嘅平台<br />\n不如就騎劫佢<br />\n每次發言都講<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求</span></span><br />\n強調返<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真普選</span></span><br />\n獨立調查委員會唔洗再emphasize<br />\n因為社會已有共識<br />\n但真普選先係解決問題嘅根源<br />\n同埋令政府最難落台<br />\n大家話係唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46b54bd1470abdf4879763d255618ca2c07ea003","tid":1598320,"uid":183734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:31:42.000Z","msg":"【重要行動/文宣】十一光復香港宣言<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1595334\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1595334</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z4kjC5T.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ4kjC5T.jpg&h=4cbee0df&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c8ec21d80c01808401e0683ef1a047dd6a2824d5","tid":1598320,"uid":104425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:33:47.000Z","msg":"928 929 101"},{"pid":"bd1400e28c51b3cc8f64bded0b7d626d3240cf20","tid":1598320,"uid":311128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T11:44:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25869952cd6c